                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "Curbside organics added to every cart customer's service. You can decline the bin but still pay the line item — same model as the existing minimum-service fee. Highest diversion potential, and Republic says the incoming EPR recycling refund could fully offset the new charge.",
