                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "AdisZ",
                  "name": "presBody",
                  "fill": "#374151",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Two presentations opened the meeting. Apex Park & Recreation District briefed council on the proposed bond package they're considering for the November ballot — full project list and tax implications attached. Following that, the city's Communications Director gave a 12-minute overview of how Arvada handled crisis communications during last month's water-main break, including response times, social-media reach, and the gaps Comms intends to address before next time.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.65,
                  "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
